					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">May 20, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/05/20/nassim-taleb-on-newsnight-talking-about-banking-risks/#respond" title="Comment on Nassim Taleb on Newsnight talking about banking&nbsp;risks.">Leave a comment</a></span>
																				</p>
					</div>

					<span class='embed-youtube' style='text-align:center; display: block;'><iframe class='youtube-player' type='text/html' width='630' height='385' src='http://www.youtube.com/embed/DjneNMNKAK8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent' frameborder='0'></iframe></span>
